{"page":2,"items":[{"id":"essays-ai-is-evolving-and-changing-our-understanding-of-intelligence","sender":"Google Paradigms of Intelligence Team","subject":"重塑 AI 的五大范式转变","snippet":"本文梳理 AI 发展中的五个范式转移，从自然计算到集体智能，讨论其对智能定义与系统设计的影响。","date":"2026-03-25","isRead":true,"isStarred":false,"hasAttachment":false,"labels":["Inbox","Essays"],"tags":["translated","ai","noema"],"mdTheme":"magazine","sourcePath":"essays/ai-is-evolving-and-changing-our-understanding-of-intelligence.md"},{"id":"talks-steve-jobs-pixar-early-days-interview-1996","sender":"Steve Jobs","subject":"史蒂夫·乔布斯谈皮克斯早期：1996 访谈","snippet":"本文整理乔布斯关于收购与运营皮克斯的访谈，覆盖创意组织、技术文化与电影工业协作。","date":"2026-03-25","isRead":true,"isStarred":false,"hasAttachment":false,"labels":["Inbox","Talks"],"tags":["translated","steve-jobs","pixar"],"mdTheme":"magazine","sourcePath":"talks/steve-jobs-pixar-early-days-interview-1996.md"},{"id":"reports-designing-ai-for-disruptive-science","sender":"Asimov Press","subject":"设计 AI 以实现颠覆性科学","snippet":"扩大AI规模是否必然带来科学的范式转变？本文以博尔赫斯的地图寓言与伦敦地铁图的演进为切入点，冷静剖析了当前AI在科研应用中的深层局限。作者指出，现有AI本质上是“预测性机器”，擅长在既有框架内累积细节，却无法像麦克斯韦方程那样，通过重构概念词汇来催生颠覆性发现。若仅止步于此，科学恐将陷入“超常态科学”的陷阱——在旧范式内的预测愈发精准，提出全新问题的能力却日益萎缩。","date":"2026-03-24","isRead":true,"isStarred":false,"hasAttachment":false,"labels":["Inbox","Reports"],"tags":["translated"],"mdTheme":"magazine","sourcePath":"reports/designing-ai-for-disruptive-science.md"},{"id":"talks-jensen-huang-nvidia-ai-revolution-lex-fridman-podcast-494","sender":"Lex Fridman","subject":"黄仁勋谈 NVIDIA 与 AI 革命（Lex Fridman","snippet":"本文整理黄仁勋长访谈，覆盖 NVIDIA 的系统级协同设计、AI 基础设施演进与组织管理方法。","date":"2026-03-24","isRead":true,"isStarred":false,"hasAttachment":false,"labels":["Inbox","Talks"],"tags":["translated","ai","nvidia"],"mdTheme":"magazine","sourcePath":"talks/jensen-huang-nvidia-ai-revolution-lex-fridman-podcast-494.md"},{"id":"talks-terence-tao-kepler-newton-and-the-true-nature-of-mathematical-discovery","sender":"Dwarkesh Patel","subject":"陶哲轩访谈：开普勒、牛顿与数学发现的真正本质","snippet":"本文整理陶哲轩访谈，讨论 AI 对