cheap-now-and-that-changes-everything","sender":"Pere Villega","subject":"代码现在很廉价，这将改变一切","snippet":"当代码生成成本被AI逼近于零，软件开发的基础逻辑正经历深远重构。本文从Kent Beck“90%技能贬值与10%技能暴涨”的洞见切入，以150美元完成35万美元项目的真实案例，揭示代码廉价化已成当下现实。作者指出，过去基于“写代码昂贵”的估算、排期等传统惯例正在失效，取而代之的是潜在软件需求的爆发。然而，代码廉价绝不意味着质量贬值。","date":"2026-03-16","isRead":true,"isStarred":false,"hasAttachment":false,"labels":["Inbox","Essays"],"tags":["translated"],"mdTheme":"magazine","sourcePath":"essays/code-is-cheap-now-and-that-changes-everything.md"},{"id":"talks-cedric-villani-the-craziest-genius-of-our-times","sender":"Turing","subject":"这个时代最疯狂的天才：塞德里克·维拉尼","snippet":"本文聚焦菲尔兹奖得主 Cedric Villani 的学术与公共行动，展现数学家如何跨越科研、政策与公众传播三重角色。","date":"2026-03-13","isRead":true,"isStarred":false,"hasAttachment":false,"labels":["Inbox","Talks"],"tags":["translated","math"],"mdTheme":"magazine","sourcePath":"talks/cedric-villani-the-craziest-genius-of-our-times.md"},{"id":"talks-oussama-khatib-shaping-the-future-of-human-robot-collaboration","sender":"Oussama Khatib","subject":"塑造人机协作的未来：Oussama Khatib","snippet":"本文整理 Khatib 教授机器人讲座，涉及深海操作、远程触觉反馈与人机协同控制框架。","date":"2026-03-13","isRead":true,"isStarred":false,"hasAttachment":false,"labels":["Inbox","Talks"],"tags":["translated","robotics"],"mdTheme":"magazine","sourcePath":"talks/oussama-khatib-shaping-the-future-of-human-robot-collaboration.md"},{"id":"essays-ai-may-be-making-us-think-and-write-more-alike","sender":"Darrin Joy","subject":"AI 可能正在让我们的思考与写作趋于同质化","snippet":"当人工智能深度融入日常，我们是否正在交出思考的独特性？南加州大学的一项最新研究指出，大型语言模型正潜移默化地使人类的表达与思考走向同质化。过度依赖AI不仅会抹平个人写作的风格个性，更在重塑我们对“正确推理”的定义。由于模型训练数据偏向特定主流文化，其所推崇的线性推理正逐渐取代直觉与抽象思维，导致全球认知多样性面临萎缩风险，进而深刻威胁人类社会的集体智慧与适应能力。","date":"2026-03-12","isRead":true,"isStarred":false,"hasAttachment":false,"labels":["Inbox","Essays"],"tags":["translated"],"mdTheme":"magazine","sourcePath":"essays/ai-may-be-making-us-think-and-write-more-alike.md"},{"id":"talks-terence-tao-mark-chen-fireside-chat-ipam-ucla","sender":"Institute for Pure & Applied Mathematics (IPAM)","subject":"陶哲轩与 Mark Chen 炉边对话：UCLA IPAM 2026","snippet":"本文记录陶哲轩与 Mark Chen 在 UCLA IPAM 的对话，聚焦 AI 在数学研究中的协作边界与工作流重构。","date":"2026-03-10","isRead":true,"isStarred":false,"hasAttachment":false,"labels":["Inbox","Talks"],"tags":["translated","ai"],"mdTheme":"magazine","sourcePath":"talks/terence-tao-mark-chen-fireside-chat-ipam-ucla.md"},{"id":"talks-leslie-lamport-thinking-clearly-paxos-raft","sender":"Ryan Peterman","subject":"图灵奖得主 Leslie Lamport：清晰思考、Paxos 与 Raft","snippet":"本文整理 Lamport 深度访谈，覆盖分布式系统思想史、Paxos 与 Raft 的差异、以及其对写作与思考方法的核心观点。","date":"2026-02-23","isRead":true,"isStarred":false,"hasAttachment":false,"labels":["Inbox","Talks"],"tags":["translated","distributed-systems"],"mdTheme":"magazine","sourcePath":"talks/leslie-lamport-thinking-clearly-paxos-raft.md"},{"id":"talks-meet-the-worlds-smartest-man","sender":"Turing","subject":"认识“世界上最聪明的人”：陶哲轩","snippet":"本文回顾陶哲轩从神童到顶尖数学家的成长轨迹，并梳理其代表性研究对现代数学与应用领域的影响。","date":"2026-02-21","isRead":true,"isStarred":false,"hasAttachment":false,"labels":["Inbox","Talks"],"tags":["translated","math","terence-tao"],"mdTheme":"magazine","sourcePath":"talks/meet-the-worlds-smartest-man.md"},{"id":"talks-head-of-claude-code-what-happens-after-coding-is-solved","sender":"Lennys Podcast","subject":"Claude Code 负责人谈：当编程被“解决”之后","snippet":"本文整理 Boris Cherny 对 AI 编程时代的判断，讨论 Agent 工作流、团队组织与软件生产方式的结构性变化。","date":"2026-02-19","isRead":true,"isStarred":false,"hasAttachment":false,"labels":["Inbox","Talks"],"tags":["translated","ai-coding"],"mdTheme":"magazine","sourcePath":"talks/head-of-claude-code-what-happens-after-coding-is-solved.md"},{"id":"talks-distinguished-colloquium-jeff-dean-february-10-2026","sender":"Princeton University Computer Science","subject":"AI 的重要趋势：我们如何走到今天、现在能做什么、未来走向何方","snippet":"本文整理 Jeff Dean 在普林斯顿的讲座实录，涵盖 Transformer 之后的模型演进、基础设施扩展与 AI 未来方向。","date":"2026-02-14","isRead":true,"isStarred":false,"hasAttachment":false,"labels":["Inbox","Talks"],"tags":["translated","ai","jeff-dean"],"mdTheme":"magazine","sourcePath":"talks/